al.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c84%2c20221207%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,111,訴,84,20221207,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"84","JDATE":"20221207","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}